# Project: {{project_name}}

## Stack
- Runtime: {{runtime}}  <!-- e.g. Bun, Node, Python -->
- Framework: {{framework}}  <!-- e.g. React + Vite, plain HTML -->
- Styling: Tailwind CSS + theme.css
- Database: SQLite (better-sqlite3 or sqlite3)
- Hosting: Vercel

## Color Palette
- Default: BB Pastel — sage greens, butter yellows, peach corals, white space
- Alt: Nord — arctic blues, cool greys, snow whites
- Set via `data-palette="bb"` or `data-palette="nord"` on root element
- Dark mode via `data-theme="dark"`
- All colors are CSS variables in theme.css. Never hardcode hex.

## Commands
- Dev: `bun dev` (or npm run dev)
- Build: `npx vercel build`
- Deploy: `npx vercel --prod`

